<li>1939 <i><a href="/wiki/Lotte_in_Weimar:_The_Beloved_Returns" title="Lotte in Weimar: The Beloved Returns">Lotte in Weimar: The Beloved Returns</a></i>, novel</li>
<li>1940 <i>The Transposed Heads</i> (<i>Die vertauschten Köpfe - Eine indische Legende</i>), novella</li>
<li>1943 <i><a href="/wiki/Listen,_Germany!" title="Listen, Germany!">Listen, Germany!</a></i> (<i>Deutsche Hörer!</i>)</li>
<li>1944 <i>Mose</i>, a commissioned novella (<i>Das Gesetz</i>, Erzählung, Auftragswerk)</li>
<li>1947 <i><a href="/wiki/Doktor_Faustus" title="Doktor Faustus" class="mw-redirect">Doctor Faustus</a></i> (<i>Doktor Faustus</i>), novel</li>
<li>1947 <i>Essays of Three Decades</i>, translated from the German by H. T. Lowe-Porter. [1st American ed.], New York, A. A. Knopf, 1947. Reprinted as Vintage book, K55, New York, <a href="/wiki/Vintage_Books" title="Vintage Books">Vintage Books</a>, 1957.</li>
<li>1951 <i><a href="/wiki/The_Holy_Sinner" title="The Holy Sinner">The Holy Sinner</a></i> (<i>Der Erwählte</i>), novel</li>
<li>1954 <i><a href="/wiki/The_Black_Swan_(Mann_novella)" title="The Black Swan (Mann novella)">The Black Swan</a></i> (<i>Die Betrogene: Erzählung</i>)</li>
<li>1954 <i><a href="/wiki/Confessions_of_Felix_Krull,_Confidence_Man:_The_Early_Years" title="Confessions of Felix Krull, Confidence Man: The Early Years" class="mw-redirect">Confessions of Felix Krull, Confidence Man: The Early Years</a></i> (<i>Bekenntnisse des Hochstaplers Felix Krull. Der Memoiren erster Teil</i>), novel expanding upon the 1911 short story, unfinished</li>
</ul>
